author: Sam McNeil / AP
title: Wuhan Celebrates the End of Its Coronavirus Lockdown After 76 Long Days
description: Chinese authorities are allowing residents of Wuhan to once again travel in and out of the sprawling city where the pandemic began.
content: (WUHAN, China) — The lockdown that served as a model for countries battling the coronavirus around the world has ended after 11 weeks: Chinese authorities are allowing residents of Wuhan to once again travel in and out of the sprawling city where the pandemic… [+4675 chars]
